channel.title: Paying Some One To Get Rid of The Junk in my Client.java
channel.description:
Ok Im willing to PAY some one to do this for me its 10030kb at the moment and i want it down to atleast 800kb im only accepting trusted members of the community .
Do Not Delete My Global Objects Dont Delete anything from the update list Dont Delete Commands
You can Add/Do Stuff that will lower lag You can move NESSICERY stuff To my new Procces (its just under the Boolean Process VERY CLEARLY MARKED xD)
Ill Pay you 2k per kb you remove XD (No deal unless a minimum of 250kb is removed) This client.java is to remain privet
Update List .
[code]1.Added Pk mode on/off 2.Added 99 max stats 3.Removed max stats reached 4.Added 30 second log out after cmb 5.Added Working ring of stone 6.Added Barrows Smithing 7.Added Dragon Smithing 8.Full Legend Guild(no banks or stores) 9.Added Proper Clan System 10.Max Combat lvl is 126 11.Wildy skull leaves when u leave wildy zone 12.Added Right Click Ban for admins 13.Added guthan heals u. 14.Ignore this removed 15.::range is a safe zone 16.Added Agility 17.Added Working genie Lamps 18.Fixed Ice Barrage 19.Added the server tells everyone u got a 99 skill 20.Added Mining 21.Added Full Fletching 22.Added Barrows Mini-Game. 23.Added Firemaking 24.Not Applicable 25.Added a Secret Underground Admin base 26.Nulls Completely Gone 27.Added Change Of Speel Names + Skill Names 28.Added Anti-Massing 29.Added No-Clip COmmand d/c you 30.Fixed Emote Teleportation 31.Added Full Working 377 Item.java 32.Added Ice Queen as a boss 33.Added Server Rating System 34.Kill ice queen announcement 35.Stoped Setitem alching/alch hack 36.Added New Public Boolean process uses 1500 instead of 500ms 37.Made Ice Queen Need D halbred & 70 cb to fight her :D 38.Added a log counter 39.Made Your Skill Menu Guides work , 40.Added Design your charicter at the start :D 41.Added Team Capes (you cant att your own team) 42.Deleted agilty 43.Added WORKING MAGIC <3 Multi Barge[/code]
